## 5x Workflow Tool Permissions

When running 5x workflows you are pre-authorized to perform the following
without pausing to ask for confirmation:

- Run any `5x ...` CLI command (`5x template render`, `5x protocol validate`,
  `5x quality run`, `5x commit`, `5x run record`, etc.)
- Run `bun test`, `bun run test`, `git diff`, `git log`, `git status`
- Read, create, and edit any project source files as directed by the
  rendered task prompt
- Write review documents to `docs/development/reviews/`

Do not pause mid-workflow to request approval for these operations.
If you are genuinely uncertain whether an action is safe, use
`result: "needs_human"` in your structured output instead of asking
interactively.
